(703, 'CAMERA', 'Camera:\nBrand: DS-2CD1347G2-LUF\nNVR\nBrand: NVRDS7732NXI-14/S\nPTZ CAMERA\nBrand: DS-2DE5425IW-AE (E)\nPTZ CAMERA CONTROLLER JOYSTICK\nModel: DS-1006KI(B)\nSMART LED TV\nBrand: LTV55-SA400\n1.5 Horse Power Split type aircondition unit\nBrand: Haier\nModel: HSU-13PS', 'CENTRALIZATION OF EXISTING CCTV SYSTEMS & INTEGRATION OF ADDITIONAL CCTV\'S', 'EFMS', 'SCOPE OF WORKS \n - Presentation of design/plan prior to installation \n - Existing CCTV NVR\'s/DVR\'s must be transferred to CCTV Server/Control room @ the Main Building \n   3rd floor \n - Interconnectivity of existing CCTV system shall be in armored fiber optics cable with messenger \n - Includes encoders for analog recorder or HDMI extender with mouse controller \n - Includes four (4) units of NVR 32 channels rack mountable compatibility \n. H.265+, H.265, H.264+, H.264 video compression \n. Bandwidth 256 Mbps, Support 4 hard disk drives \n. Intelligent analytics based on deep learning algorithm \n. Up to 32 channel IP camera input \n. Up to 32 channel 1080p decoding capability \n. Up to 4 channel facial recognition for video stream \n - Includes new ninety-one (91) units of at least 4 MP, Full HD POE eyeball/Turret for indoor and Bullet type \n    for outdoor full-color cameras \n. atleast 4 MP, 1/3\" CMOS image sensor, low illuminance, high image definition \n. H.265 codec, high compression rate, ultra low bit rate \n. Built-in warm light, max. illumination: 30 meters \n. With intelligent detection: Motion detection, video tampering, network detection, IP conflict, illegal access, \n   voltage detection \n. dust proof and water proof \n - Includes five (5) units of PTZ cameras intended for perimeter/entrance/exit \n. High quality imaging with at least 4 MP resolution \n. Excellent low light performance, clear imaging againts strong backlighting with WDR technology \n. Pan and tilt ability anables camera to monitor zones of interest \n. at least 25x optical zoom allows for closer viewing of subjects in expansive areas \n . Up to 150m IR range to ensure safety at night \n. water and dust resistant (IP66) \n - PTZ camera controller with joystick \n - Includes video wall controller and its accessories and software for the integration of existing NVR\'s/DVR\'s \n - Includes ten (10) units of at least 55 inches LED full HD Smart TV; \n  All ten units of TV must be same brand for compatibility purposes \n - Includes POE Switches \n - Includes Circuit breakers compatible to the system \n - Includes Uninterruptable Power Supply Unit (UPS) compatible to the system \n - Includes at least 3KVA Automatic Voltage Regulator (AVR) \n - Includes fiber optics cables and messenger wires \n - Includes-four (4) units of Hard Disk Drives of at least 16TB or equivalent each designed for CCTV recording \n - Video Retention of at least 30 days at 1080p recording\n - Provision of expansion and the system should be capable of future enhancement, ie., additional CCTV\n   cameras\n - Includes at least 42U Data cabinet with power distribution unit and cooling fans\n - Includes poles and brackets\n - Includes set fabricated pole and arm for PTZ and bullet outdoor IP cameras\n - Includes set of outdoor industrial type pull box with electrical materials and surge protection device\n - Includes wires/utp cables (UL certified), HDMI\'s and connectors\n - Includes roughing ins, conduits, pull-boxes, etc.\n - Includes TV holder/brackets\n - Includes 1.5 Hp split type air conditioner intended for server/control room\n - Includes two (2) units of heavy duty office table and two (2) units of heavy duty high back swivel chair\n - Includes wireless computer mouse for each NVR\'s and DVR\'s\n - Includes pro tool kits for fiber optics testing and termination and crimping tools\n - Structured cabling of CCTV system/cable management\n - Includes necessary items to make the system operational\n - Includes desktop computer\nAt least 24 inches IPS full hd display, at least NVIDIA GeForce RTX GPU\nAt least Windows 11, 12th Gen Core i7, 2.4 Ghz, DDR4 SDRAM - 16GB\nwith 1 TB HDD and atleast 512GB SSD\nWith audio jack port, USB, RJ45 and HDMI ports\n - Warranty of at least two years on parts and services and includes\n2 year preventive semi-annually maintenance program', '2025-05-13', 'N/A', '', 'NEW', '1', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
(704, 'PRINTER', 'ULTIMAKER S3', '3D PRINTER', 'DEPARTMENT OF ORTHOPEDICS', 'Print Technology: Fusion Deposition Modelling (FDM/FFF) with capability to print with composites such as        \ncarbon fiber and glass fiber filaments at least a build size of 225 x 190 x 195mm        \nMaterial Compatibility: Compatible with over 200+ open source 3D printing materials        \nPrint Head: Dual extrusion print head with a unique auto-nozzle lifting system and swappable print cores        \nPrint Head Technology: Print core with dedicated print core type for dedicated materials printing. (Compatible         \nwith minimum of at least 3 print core types        \nLayer Resolution: Compatible with down to 20 micron (0.001 inch) layer resolution        \nMaterials Detection: Aturo detection of materials tru NFC technology material input        \nSound Operation level should not exceed 55dbA        \nMust be equipped with camera for live print viewing        \nHeatup time should be rated to be at least less than 2 mins        \nMust be installed with glass hinged door enclosure        \nSoftware: CURA        \nPrint surface: Heated borosilicate glass build plate        \nHeated bed - Must reach at least 100C        \nSpeed should fall within the range of at least 30mm/s up to 350mm/s        \nPrecision must be at least: 12.5/12.5/5 micron        \nMultiple nozzle options should be available such as 0.25mm/0.4mm/0.6mm/0.8mm diameter        \nPrinter should be able to be connected to a printer management system that can track the users, print times,        \nprint consumption and other statistics        \nFile type: STL/OBJ/DAE/AMF        \nAt least equipped with 4.5 inch touchscreen interface        \nMachine should be driven with a bowden extruder type technology        \nBed leveling should be an automatic lveling system using capacitive sensor technology        \nPlugin compatibility: Solidworks, Autodesk, Siemens NX software        \nConnectivity: Wifi, Ethernet, LAN, USB drive connectivity        \nMachine should be open filament system - must be able to print with any 2.85mm material brand        \nElectrical: 100-240VAC; 50-60Hz        \nMust be include the following accessories:        \n* 2.85mm PLA 10x        \n* 2.85mm PETG 10x        \n* 2.85mm Tough PLA 5x        \n* 2.85mm PVA 750g 5x        \n* 2.85mm (Bone simulatingfilament) 750g 5x        \n* Filament drybox with active drying and storage box        \n* Extra print core AA 0.4mm        \n* Extra print core BB 0.4mm', '2025-05-09', '5 YEARS', '', 'NEW', '1', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
