(724, 'ENTERPRISE ROUTER', 'TPLINK', 'ENTERPRISE ROUTER (MULTI-GIGABIT VPN ROUTER)', 'IHOMP', '- Two 2.5G Ports:1x2.5G WAN and 1x2.5G WAN/LAN ports provide high bandwidth aggregation connectivity\n - Up to 6 WAN ports: 2.5G RJ45, gigabit fiber, and gigabit RJ45 WAN ports with load balance raise the\n   utilization rate of multi-line boradband\n - Highly secure VPN: Enterprise-standard\n - SSL/IPSec/GER§/PPTP/L2TP VPN & OpenVPN are ideal for use accross multiple branches and for WFH\n - Centralized Management: Cloud access and (preferably) Omada app provide the utmost in management\n    convenience\n - Access control source/Destination IP based access control\nFiltering• WEB group filtering\nARP Inspection• URL filtering\nWeb security\nSending GARP Packets\nARP Scanning\nIP-MAC binding\nAttack Defense• TCP/UDP/ICMP Flood defense\nBlock TCP Scan (Stealth FIN/Xmas/Null)\nBlock ping from WAN\nInterface• 1x2.5G RJ45 WAN Port\n1x2.5G RJ45 WAN/LAN Port\n1x Gigabit SFP WAN/LAN Port\n4x Gigabit RJ45 WAN/LAN Ports\n1x USB 2.0 port (Supports USB storage, and LTE backup with LTE dongle)\nNetwork Media•10BASE-T:UTP category 3,4,5 cable (max 100m) EIA/TIA-568 100Ω STP (Max 100 m)\n100BASE-TX: UTP category 5, 5e cable (max 100 m)\nEIA/TIA - 568 100Ω STP (Max 100 m)\n1000BASE-T: UTP category 5, 5e, 6 cable (Max 100 m)\n2500BASE-T: UTP category 5, 5e, 6 cable (Max 100 m)\nFan quantity    Fanless\nButtonReset Button\nPower Supply12V/1.5A Adapter\nFlash125MB NAND\nDRAM1 GB DDR4\nOneModify WAN/LAN MAC Address†\nDHCP• DHCP Server', '2025-09-05', '5  YEARS', '', 'NEW', '5', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
(725, 'UPS', 'INVT POWER', '20kVA SINGLE PHASE UNINTERRUPTIBLE POWER SUPPLY (UPS)', 'IHOMP', 'Nominal voltage: 220V/240V\nInput voltage range: 110-300V (Based on load at 50%)\n176-300V (based on load at 100%)\nFrequency range: 40 to 70 Hz\nPower factor: >0.99 at nominal voltage (100% load)\nOutput:\nOutput voltage: 220V/230V/240V\nVoltage regulation: + 1%\nFrequency range (syncronized mode): 50/60 Hz+/-3Hz\nFrenquency range (battery mode): 50/60 Hz+/-0.1Hz\nCurrent crest ratio: 3:1\nTransfer time AC to battery mode: zero\nTransfer time to inverter to bypass: zero\nWaveform (battery mode): Pure sinewave\nBattery type:\nMaintenance free sealed lead-acid battery with suspended electrolyte, leak proof\nSurge energy rating: at least 600 joules', '2025-09-09', '5  YEARS', '', 'NEW', '1', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
(726, 'NETWORK SWITCH', 'TPLINK SG6654X', 'MANAGEABLE SWITCH', 'IHOMP', '48XGigabit RJ45 ports and 6x10 gbps\nSFP+slots\n216 Gbps switching capacity per unit\nPhysical stacking for built-in redundancy and performance\nL3 features: RIP, OSPF, ECMP, VRRP, PIM-DM, DHCP Server/Relay\nSecurity strategies: ACL, Port security, Dos Defend, 802.1x\nHighly available with two internet fixed power supplies, VRRP, and ERPS\nCentralized cloud management via Omada\nController standalone management via WEB, CLI, SNMP, and RMON.', '2025-09-17', '5  YEARS', '', 'NEW', '2', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
