(731, 'PHOTOCOPIER', 'GESTETNER/RICOH M2810N', 'PHOTOCOPIER MACHINE WITH AUTOMATIC REVERSE DOCUMENT FEEDER', 'BILLING', 'B/W Copier, Printer and Scanner with Automatic Reverse Document\nFeeder and Two (2) Paper Feed Tray\nFeatures: Print/scan/copy\nWarm-up time: 15 seconds\nFirst Output speed: 6.4 seconds\nContinous output speed: 28 ppm\nMemory: 512 MB\nARDF capacity: 50 sheets\nRecommended paper size: B5 to A3\nPower source: 220 - 240 V, 50/60Hz\nCopier:\nMiltiple copying: up to 999 copies\nResolution scanning: -150 x 150 dpi (black and white)\n                                  - 200 x 200 dpi (grayscale, colour)\nResolution printing: -2400 x 600 dpi (with smoothing)\nZoom: Platen (From 25% to 400% in 1% steps)\nARDF (from 25% to 200% in 1% steps)\nPrinter:\nPrinter language: Standard: PCL 5, PCL 6 (XL)\nPrint Resolution: 2400 x 600 dpi with smoothing\nNetwork interface: High speed USB 2.0\nEthernet 10 base - T/100 base -TX\nWindows environment: Windows R, 10, 11\nWindows R server 2012/R2, 2016, 2019, 2022\nScanner:\nScanning speed: 24 ipm/25ipm (colour/B&W)\n18ipm - Network TWAIN\nResolution: Maximum: MMR/JPEG\nFile formats: Single page TIFF, Multi Page TIFF\nSingle Page: JPEG\nSinglePage: PDF\nScan Modes: Folder USB\nSupplier\'s Offer with free: 2 crtgs toner for M2810N\n2 pcs Cabinet\n2 pcs LAN Cable/USB Cable\nAfter sales service: Lifetime free monthly service\nMachine Guarantee: 1 year or 60,000 copies whichever comes first', '2025-10-13', '5  YEARS', '', 'NEW', '2', 'CHARLEMAGNE T. VILLACORTE'),
